BulkUploadForEntAppointment.String5: UK  UK  5. The current time format is a {{timeFormat}} e g. {{currentTime}}.
BulkUploadForEntAppointment.String6: UK  UK  6. Save the file after filling it with data.
BulkUploadForEntAppointment.String7: UK  UK  7. Click on the Choose File button and select the excel sheet.
BulkUploadForEntAppointment.String8: UK  UK  8. Click on the Upload button.
BulkUploadForEntAppointment.String9: UK  UK  9. Your appointments will be seen in the dashboard.
